WEBVTT

01:38.240 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 8

01:49.640 --> 01:51.920
What's this?

01:54.160 --> 01:56.880
Don't snoop! Give it back.

01:59.680 --> 02:01.200
It's Yixiao Naihe!

02:05.000 --> 02:08.520
Ms. Weiwei, you're such a fangirl.

02:09.120 --> 02:12.160
Last time, your eyes sparkled,
when I mentioned Xiao Nai.

02:13.280 --> 02:15.360
You're the same with Yixiao Naihe.

02:16.120 --> 02:20.720
That's not the same.
I look up to Xiao Nai professionally.

02:21.240 --> 02:22.720
I worship him.

02:24.520 --> 02:26.120
As for Yixiao Naihe...

02:27.240 --> 02:28.280
What's Yixiao Naihe to you?

02:30.040 --> 02:30.880
A good friend.

02:36.920 --> 02:39.200
Why can't we watch the points game?

02:39.280 --> 02:43.600
Must single guys like us
play among ourselves outside?

02:43.840 --> 02:46.240
The game probably wants to charge for it.

02:46.320 --> 02:48.520
That's why they're so cruel and spiteful.

02:49.280 --> 02:50.560
Xiaoyu Yaoyao and the others are here.

02:56.400 --> 02:59.360
Yaoyao is glaring at me.

02:59.960 --> 03:02.640
I should really pray
for Xiaoyu Yaoyao and Zhenshui Wuxiang.

03:03.360 --> 03:05.160
Whose side are you on?

03:05.760 --> 03:07.360
I pray they encounter Nai
in the first round.

03:07.920 --> 03:08.840
That's more like it.

03:17.040 --> 03:19.840
I hope we don't go up against
Xiaoyu Yaoyao in round one.

03:22.360 --> 03:24.520
It's time. Let's go in.

03:24.960 --> 03:25.800
Okay.

03:28.080 --> 03:29.760
Houzi, give me the remote control.

03:47.800 --> 03:51.080
Yugong can be a fortune-teller
or a diviner.

03:52.920 --> 03:55.240
The first round of In-Game Couples
Battle Championship starts now.

03:55.320 --> 03:57.080
You have three minutes to prepare.

04:03.600 --> 04:05.280
I'll take out Xiaoyu Yaoyao first.

04:07.520 --> 04:10.840
Xiaoyu Yaoyao is the weakest,
and her character is a doctor.

04:10.920 --> 04:12.840
Against you,
she won't even have a chance to strike.

04:13.800 --> 04:16.680
It's good that you take her out.
It'll be faster that way,

04:16.760 --> 04:22.160
but won't the Xiaoyus use this incident
to say that you bully a weak girl?

04:22.240 --> 04:23.800
Does killing them require an explanation?

04:26.000 --> 04:29.520
Fine, let's begin. It won't break a sweat.

04:32.960 --> 04:33.840
Wait.

04:37.480 --> 04:40.680
Why don't I take them on?
If I'm in trouble, you can jump in?

04:56.760 --> 04:58.720
Did they run away?

05:00.640 --> 05:01.920
Yes, they're gone.

05:04.680 --> 05:07.520
It's our first game
and our opponents ran away.

05:08.600 --> 05:10.400
Are we that scary?

05:10.760 --> 05:13.560
They must be more terrified of you.

05:15.640 --> 05:17.280
First round of points game,

05:17.360 --> 05:21.400
Yixiao Naihe and Luwei Weiwei win,
receiving three points.

05:27.840 --> 05:30.160
The second round of In-Game Couples
Battle Championship starts now.

05:30.240 --> 05:32.320
You have three minutes to prepare.

05:41.000 --> 05:42.600
Familiar faces again?

05:45.560 --> 05:48.160
Diemeng Weixing is the former leader
of my old clan.

05:48.640 --> 05:51.360
We used to be good friends,

05:52.360 --> 05:54.720
but later Diemeng quit the game,

05:54.800 --> 05:57.120
and handed the clan over to Zhan Tianxia.

05:59.000 --> 06:01.400
I didn't expect to run into you, Weiwei.

06:02.400 --> 06:03.680
I know, what a coincidence!

06:04.640 --> 06:08.880
- Are you back, Diemeng?
- Yes, I'm back.

06:09.160 --> 06:10.880
It's such a bustling competition.
I can't miss out.

06:13.000 --> 06:15.520
The second points game starts now.

06:37.320 --> 06:38.720
Yixiao Naihe and Luwei Weiwei

06:38.800 --> 06:42.320
win the second points game,
receiving three points.

06:53.000 --> 06:54.600
Weiwei, do you have time to talk?

06:57.000 --> 06:57.840
Sure.

07:07.160 --> 07:10.640
Do you remember? This is where we met.

07:11.200 --> 07:13.480
I was on a quest to kill an elite boss.

07:13.680 --> 07:15.000
I was stuck on it.

07:15.640 --> 07:17.360
One time, I was going to die again,

07:17.440 --> 07:19.960
when you suddenly descended from the sky
and joined my team.

07:21.880 --> 07:25.280
That time? I was also on a quest.

07:26.480 --> 07:28.520
Those were happy days.

07:28.600 --> 07:30.280
We trained every day
and explored the instance dungeon.

07:35.600 --> 07:38.120
I looked into that dispute earlier,

07:38.440 --> 07:39.600
and I've scolded Tianxia.

07:40.120 --> 07:42.320
But, I still need to apologize to you.

07:44.800 --> 07:47.280
Diemeng, that had nothing to do with you.

07:47.360 --> 07:48.480
You don't need to apologize to me.

07:49.360 --> 07:51.040
Of course, it has to do with me.

07:51.120 --> 07:54.000
I handed the clan over to Tianxia,
after all.

07:54.800 --> 07:58.520
Now that I'm back,
you should return to the clan, Weiwei.

08:01.600 --> 08:05.440
With so many exams coming up,
I'd rather not spend too much time gaming.

08:05.800 --> 08:09.360
Forget everything else, I only want to
play the in-game couples championship.

08:17.200 --> 08:20.360
There's something I heard...

08:22.800 --> 08:27.160
- Are you going to say Xiaoyu Qingqing?
- You've heard?

08:28.600 --> 08:31.400
Of course. Don't worry, I'll handle her.

08:31.720 --> 08:34.360
She can't wreck
my relationship with Tianxia.

08:35.080 --> 08:36.440
I never told you,

08:36.520 --> 08:38.919
but he's my boyfriend in real life, too.

08:39.400 --> 08:41.400
Why else would I hand over
the clan to him?

08:44.200 --> 08:47.600
I see. That's good, then.

08:54.160 --> 08:56.400
In the blink of an eye, June is upon us.

08:57.080 --> 09:00.680
Soon, the seniors will be leaving school,

09:01.160 --> 09:03.640
rushing toward their next journey.

09:06.680 --> 09:09.480
We've reached our server's final, too.

09:09.560 --> 09:10.840
It's today.

09:11.800 --> 09:16.000
That's how I am, a master of
both pen and sword, wise and fierce.

09:17.000 --> 09:19.440
Bei Weiwei,

09:19.520 --> 09:23.520
I was going to treat you to a hot pot meal
after the College English Test Band 6.

09:24.280 --> 09:27.200
Now, it looks like I can save that money.

09:29.240 --> 09:30.080
Xiaoling.

09:31.080 --> 09:33.200
Xiaoling. Do you want a drink?

09:33.280 --> 09:37.760
- Boost magic points, be super Xiaoling!
- Gross.

09:38.240 --> 09:40.840
Fine. Go take part in your competition.

09:41.440 --> 09:46.080
- Is the hot pot still on?
- Yes.

09:49.080 --> 09:51.720
How come Diemeng Weixing
and Zhan Tianxia still haven't shown up?

09:51.800 --> 09:53.920
We're finally able to come
watch the final.

09:54.000 --> 09:56.160
Are they going to be late?

09:56.240 --> 09:58.080
Are they not coming at all?

09:59.000 --> 10:00.440
Since they lost the points game,

10:00.520 --> 10:03.440
and now they have to face Luwei Weiwei
and Yixiao Naihe again...

10:03.800 --> 10:06.160
Maybe they're scared,
so they're not coming?

10:06.240 --> 10:07.640
- Right!
- No way!

10:07.720 --> 10:11.040
- They can't show cowardice.
- Right?

10:11.120 --> 10:12.320
It can't be?

10:12.640 --> 10:14.200
On Capital City Bests Server,

10:14.280 --> 10:16.760
the final of In-Game Couples
Battle Championship starts now.

10:16.840 --> 10:18.960
You have three minutes to prepare.

10:21.080 --> 10:21.960
Why aren't they here yet?

10:22.800 --> 10:26.240
When the three minutes are up,
they'll be disqualified.

10:30.000 --> 10:31.720
Fate brings couples together
and tears couples apart.

10:32.280 --> 10:34.640
Diemeng Weixing and Zhan Tianxia
have fallen out of love.

10:34.720 --> 10:36.440
They have annulled their in-game marriage.

10:36.520 --> 10:39.360
They are now unattached to each other.

10:40.080 --> 10:44.040
Darn it! Why didn't you annul it sooner?
We paid to come watch the final!

10:46.000 --> 10:48.040
Yixiao Naihe and Luwei Weiwei

10:48.120 --> 10:50.800
win the final of In-Game Couples
Battle Championship,

10:50.880 --> 10:54.240
as well as the In-Game Couples Battle
Championship on Capital City Bests Server.

10:54.320 --> 10:56.640
They advance into the overall qualifiers.

10:57.040 --> 11:01.480
They'll represent this server and compete
against top placers from all servers.

11:02.720 --> 11:06.360
- Let's go.
- I'll go ask Leishen Nini what happened.

11:06.440 --> 11:09.080
- You should go join Yugong and others.
- Okay.

11:20.480 --> 11:21.680
Weiwei, here you are!

11:21.760 --> 11:23.600
Nini, I tried to text Diemeng,

11:23.680 --> 11:26.800
- but her decline-all setting blocked it.
- I had the same problem.

11:26.880 --> 11:28.040
I asked around the clan.

11:28.120 --> 11:29.680
It's that witch, Xiaoyu Qingqing again.

11:30.280 --> 11:32.440
The entire public chat room
is talking about this.

11:33.040 --> 11:35.960
It seems Clan Leader Diemeng tried to
kick Xiaoyu Qingqing out of the clan,

11:36.480 --> 11:38.000
but Zhan Tianxia disagreed.
They're why they fought.

11:39.440 --> 11:41.680
Why do the Xiaoyus
always do stuff like that?

12:12.400 --> 12:14.280
Yixiao Naihe and Luwei Weiwei

12:14.360 --> 12:16.280
win the semi-final
of In-Game Couples Battle Championship,

12:16.360 --> 12:18.160
advancing into the all-servers final.

12:18.240 --> 12:21.240
They will compete for the all-servers
championship title tomorrow night.

12:39.520 --> 12:40.760
Way to go.

12:41.040 --> 12:43.280
You'll win the championship tomorrow!
Nai's treating us!

12:46.280 --> 12:49.640
Getting into the final is no guarantee
for the title, right?

12:50.320 --> 12:54.160
You'll win for sure.
Have more confidence in yourself, okay?

12:54.240 --> 12:56.640
I did some research.
Your opponents may be good,

12:57.280 --> 12:58.760
but they're out of luck.

12:58.960 --> 13:00.520
Your skills are effective
against their occupations.

13:02.160 --> 13:05.480
Fine, I'll eat more tomorrow,

13:05.560 --> 13:08.520
so I'll have more energy to fight.
Is that okay?

13:10.240 --> 13:11.080
Naihe?

13:14.720 --> 13:16.000
Nai went to make a call.

13:22.720 --> 13:23.680
He's back.

13:25.000 --> 13:27.280
Weiwei, I have a business dinner tomorrow.

13:27.360 --> 13:30.280
- I might be a little late.
- I'll come a bit late, too.

13:30.360 --> 13:32.720
- Half past seven, at the latest.
- Okay.

13:33.960 --> 13:35.760
They must be chatting privately.

13:38.560 --> 13:42.360
Hello? Shaoxiang,
Qingqing is giving me grief again.

13:42.440 --> 13:45.000
She says, we didn't fight
Luwei Weiwei and Yixiao Naihe,

13:45.080 --> 13:48.280
now they won the server championship
and got into the final.

13:49.120 --> 13:51.320
So what if they win
the all-servers championship?

13:51.400 --> 13:53.400
They're still losers in real life.

13:53.480 --> 13:55.320
Don't be upset. Hubby loves you.

13:57.280 --> 14:00.400
I'm not upset. It's Qingqing who's upset.

14:00.840 --> 14:02.680
Can you believe Luwei Weiwei?

14:02.760 --> 14:04.720
Qingqing is a girl, after all.

14:04.800 --> 14:06.040
How can she treat her like that?

14:06.880 --> 14:09.680
Not all women are softhearted
and kind like you.

14:09.760 --> 14:11.080
I'm so lucky, Yaoyao.

14:13.760 --> 14:14.600
Come on, call me Hubby.

14:15.240 --> 14:16.600
You're naughty.

14:18.160 --> 14:20.120
Why don't I take you to
a Japanese restaurant this weekend?

14:20.880 --> 14:21.880
Sure.

14:23.080 --> 14:26.120
- I want to go shopping, too.
- Shopping? Sure.

14:26.200 --> 14:29.040
I'll buy all the clothes and purses
you like, okay?

14:29.480 --> 14:31.840
There you go again, Shaoxiang.

14:31.920 --> 14:34.120
Those things aren't the reason
why I'm with you.

14:34.640 --> 14:37.200
Yes, I understand. I'm sorry.

14:39.480 --> 14:42.960
- I have a call. I'll call you back.
- Okay.

14:55.160 --> 14:56.080
Yes?

14:56.800 --> 14:58.120
Sir, Mr. Zhen is on the line for you.

15:00.160 --> 15:01.960
- Put him through.
- Okay.

15:04.240 --> 15:06.120
Hello? Who are you on the phone with?

15:06.200 --> 15:07.920
I've been trying your cell for ages.

15:09.600 --> 15:13.440
- A girl. Is that okay?
- You...

15:13.920 --> 15:16.360
When will you grow up?

15:16.800 --> 15:19.920
You've been at the office for a while now.
How are you settling in?

15:20.760 --> 15:23.360
Dad, you make me come to the office
every day,

15:23.440 --> 15:26.080
just to sign some unimportant documents?

15:26.280 --> 15:29.360
Haven't I made myself clear?

15:29.640 --> 15:32.000
I let you roam free,
when all you did was play.

15:32.560 --> 15:36.440
Now, it's time to focus
and learn to manage the company.

15:36.880 --> 15:39.960
Eventually,
all of this will be passed to you.

15:41.680 --> 15:42.880
Learn to manage?

15:42.960 --> 15:45.600
I feel like all I do here
is practice my penmanship.

15:47.960 --> 15:51.680
The finals are later this year.
I won't be going home until July.

15:53.480 --> 15:54.960
I already bought the tickets.

15:55.200 --> 15:56.720
I booked them online.

15:58.200 --> 16:01.440
You don't have to pick me up
at the station. I can carry it myself.

16:01.920 --> 16:05.720
Anyway, it's not the weekend.
You both have to work.

16:07.600 --> 16:09.160
Okay, bye-bye.

16:12.080 --> 16:15.440
My goodness! I got an email
from Zhenyi Tech!

16:15.520 --> 16:16.480
Could it be...

16:17.880 --> 16:20.400
It's true! I got hired!

16:21.080 --> 16:25.400
I can't believe there's a company willing
to take in someone... A talent like me.

16:26.560 --> 16:31.040
- It's Zhenyi Tech?
- Yes. Check your emails.

16:35.000 --> 16:36.520
I... I didn't get it.

16:37.880 --> 16:40.680
Me, neither. What about you, Weiwei?

16:41.080 --> 16:43.720
Hold on... No.

16:44.720 --> 16:48.040
You didn't get the email?
Only I got the email?

16:48.200 --> 16:49.760
That's impossible.

16:50.440 --> 16:53.840
- Refresh it again.
- I've refreshed it many times.

16:55.880 --> 17:00.120
It's okay. It's a big company.
Maybe they send the emails separately.

17:00.520 --> 17:04.520
- This is usually done by mass email.
- It's got to be mass email.

17:06.200 --> 17:08.200
Am I really the only one who got in?

17:09.680 --> 17:12.200
It may be incredulous,

17:12.280 --> 17:14.520
but that seems to be the fact.

17:15.319 --> 17:16.880
My goodness!

17:17.160 --> 17:18.960
Given Erxi's outfit that day,

17:19.680 --> 17:23.319
just what kind of hiring standard
does this company have?

17:24.440 --> 17:28.560
I told you,
we should dress like geeky girls,

17:28.720 --> 17:30.640
to show our steely sincerity.

17:30.880 --> 17:34.760
You didn't believe me,
now you're kicking yourselves.

17:36.360 --> 17:40.040
Wait, I don't have
enough outfits like that.

17:40.440 --> 17:42.920
I won't have enough clothes to wear
when the internship starts.

17:43.200 --> 17:46.440
- Why don't you come shopping with me?
- Sure.

17:46.520 --> 17:49.760
- I need some normal clothes, too.
- I'll come, too!

17:50.600 --> 17:52.000
You guys go. I'll pass.

17:52.720 --> 17:55.320
I'm not interested
in shopping for clothes.

17:55.400 --> 17:57.840
- I need a refill.
- Just think of it as exercise.

17:57.920 --> 18:01.560
It's not healthy
to sit in front of a computer every day.

18:02.560 --> 18:04.360
How dare you say exercise?

18:04.440 --> 18:07.480
Who asks me to help her
beep her jogging card every morning?

18:07.560 --> 18:10.640
Who forgets to refill the water cooler
every day and asks me to do it?

18:12.080 --> 18:13.200
Weiwei!

18:13.480 --> 18:16.040
What you're wearing now
is from last year, right?

18:16.120 --> 18:17.480
- May I have some water?
- Go get new clothes.

18:17.560 --> 18:18.400
Sure.

18:18.840 --> 18:20.520
I'm content with enough clothes to wear.

18:21.080 --> 18:24.560
It's a shame to hear a beauty like you
say something like that.

18:24.840 --> 18:28.040
If you keep this up, you'll get kicked off
the campus beauty list eventually.

18:30.200 --> 18:33.880
That'd be the best.
I only care about inner beauty.

18:34.920 --> 18:37.640
Don't poke her where it hurts.

18:37.840 --> 18:40.320
She never liked that campus beauty list.

18:40.400 --> 18:44.520
Lately, there's even a worse thing,
called the risk index list.

18:45.000 --> 18:48.200
Weiwei got voted to the top
of that risk index list,

18:48.280 --> 18:50.280
saying that she's most likely to cheat.

18:54.400 --> 18:55.720
When was that?

18:57.320 --> 18:59.200
Why didn't you tell me?

18:59.280 --> 19:02.200
When it's something you can't change,
it's best not to know.

19:05.560 --> 19:06.640
So depressing.

19:06.960 --> 19:08.480
I wish I had the skills to hack the forum.

19:09.360 --> 19:13.920
It's okay. Let's blow off some steam
by going shopping.

19:15.560 --> 19:16.960
I'm not going.

19:17.040 --> 19:19.680
I have a gaming final
at eight o'clock tonight.

19:20.240 --> 19:23.600
It's at eight. What's the hurry?
It's only five now.

19:23.840 --> 19:26.640
Go shopping, eat,
then come back and fight.

19:27.760 --> 19:28.800
Bei Weiwei,

19:29.480 --> 19:33.480
if you refuse to go,
it'll be corporal punishment tonight.

19:37.560 --> 19:41.440
If you don't come with us,
who will do the bargaining? Come on!

19:43.680 --> 19:45.920
That's the real reason
why you want me to go, right?

19:46.120 --> 19:47.320
Let's go.

19:49.080 --> 19:50.880
Welcome. Please come in.

19:52.280 --> 19:53.880
Why do I have to carry your bags?

19:53.960 --> 19:57.680
Because you won't buy anything,
so you have to be our sidekick.

20:03.520 --> 20:05.960
Am I destined to be a sidekick?

20:06.280 --> 20:07.880
It's been like that in the game, too.

20:08.320 --> 20:11.560
Naihe has been bossing me around
more and more.

20:11.840 --> 20:14.240
Enough, don't complain.

20:14.720 --> 20:18.160
Since you saved me so much money today,

20:18.760 --> 20:23.000
I'll treat you to red wine chicken wings
from House of Tianxiang.

20:23.080 --> 20:23.920
Will that do?

20:24.440 --> 20:27.040
- I worked hard. I want half the wings.
- No problem.

20:27.120 --> 20:30.520
You can have them all.
I won't fight you for them. I'm on a diet.

20:31.520 --> 20:33.560
I never put on weight. Eat my shorts.

20:34.320 --> 20:38.000
Shut the door, Xiaoling.
Let Erxi out. Bite her!

20:55.760 --> 20:56.720
- Who's that?
- Isn't that Xiao Nai?

20:56.800 --> 20:59.960
I had a great time.
I hope to meet with you again.

21:00.040 --> 21:00.920
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

21:05.560 --> 21:06.760
What are they doing?

21:07.320 --> 21:08.720
He's so handsome!

21:10.400 --> 21:12.400
Catch up to him.

21:18.080 --> 21:19.160
He turned around!

21:24.920 --> 21:27.400
Was he looking at me? Was he?

21:27.760 --> 21:29.160
Did you see that? Did you?

21:35.640 --> 21:38.160
Why didn't we come here sooner?

21:38.240 --> 21:41.360
We might have been able
to have dinner with Xiao Nai!

21:41.440 --> 21:42.600
In your dreams.

21:42.840 --> 21:45.160
Mr. Xiao was hanging out with grown-ups.

21:45.240 --> 21:47.320
They must have met in a private room.

21:48.640 --> 21:51.320
That's it. I have something to tell you.

21:52.120 --> 21:55.440
Mr. Xiao's company seems to be in trouble.

21:55.520 --> 21:56.400
No way!

21:56.880 --> 21:58.600
I heard it from Dazhong,

21:58.680 --> 22:00.200
a member of his basketball team

22:00.280 --> 22:02.040
who has worked at Mr. Xiao's company
since he graduated.

22:02.840 --> 22:05.400
They went drinking a few days ago.

22:05.480 --> 22:08.040
He got drunk and let slip something.

22:08.120 --> 22:11.960
He said there's something wrong
with the investors.

22:12.440 --> 22:13.920
That was only a few days ago.

22:14.000 --> 22:16.960
I still can't quite believe it.
It's Xiao Nai!

22:17.240 --> 22:20.240
If "bull" is a word for someone
who's clever and powerful,

22:20.320 --> 22:21.960
then Xiao Nai is a "rare bull."

22:22.240 --> 22:25.480
A rarity among the most powerful of bulls.

22:25.560 --> 22:27.360
There's something he can't handle?

22:27.680 --> 22:30.640
Investors? So, it's about funding?

22:31.120 --> 22:32.480
I don't know.

22:33.520 --> 22:36.520
I can't promise the news is credible,

22:37.280 --> 22:40.000
but whether it's fake or not,
you can't breathe a word.

22:41.520 --> 22:44.120
I promise I won't. It'll digest away
with the dinner we're about to have.

22:45.240 --> 22:47.720
Enough about that. I'm starving.
Let's head in.

22:48.080 --> 22:51.200
Let's wish all of us can pass
the College English Test Band 6,

22:51.280 --> 22:53.240
and begin our ascent to life's heights.

22:53.640 --> 22:54.920
- Let's go!
- Go!

22:55.000 --> 22:55.840
Let's eat.

23:05.240 --> 23:06.480
You were right.

23:06.560 --> 23:09.360
They're sabotaging our financing,
pulling the "rag" from under our feet.

23:11.480 --> 23:12.880
Pulling the rug from under one's feet.

23:14.040 --> 23:14.880
Right.

23:15.760 --> 23:16.920
My goodness!

23:17.240 --> 23:20.920
I almost used the right idiom this time!
I've improved.

23:22.160 --> 23:23.520
Thankfully we have plenty of cards.

23:24.080 --> 23:28.120
Nai, when are you going
to meet with Fengteng in Shanghai?

23:28.800 --> 23:29.800
There's no hurry.

23:31.320 --> 23:35.640
By the way, that was the department belle
standing across the street from us.

23:35.920 --> 23:37.800
Has Cupid been favoring me lately?

23:38.000 --> 23:39.920
I've been running into her a lot.

23:40.000 --> 23:42.640
Does this seem like
the beginning of something?

23:43.360 --> 23:46.520
Even if it is,
it has nothing to do with you.

23:47.480 --> 23:48.640
Hey!

23:48.720 --> 23:51.760
Can't a guy dream a little?
Why do you care?

23:52.760 --> 23:55.800
Anyway, it doesn't have to be
the department belle.

23:55.880 --> 23:59.200
Look at me, I'll start working soon.

23:59.280 --> 24:00.920
When I put on a suit,

24:01.000 --> 24:03.880
and give a speech at ChinaJoy,

24:03.960 --> 24:06.560
maybe a model will be attracted to me?

24:10.360 --> 24:11.440
Watch out!

24:19.000 --> 24:21.760
Why are you running, Weiwei?

24:22.080 --> 24:24.200
It's getting late. I have a final to play.

24:24.280 --> 24:27.280
You're crazy.
Doesn't the final start at eight o'clock?

24:27.840 --> 24:29.840
I'm meeting him at half past seven.
I can't be late.

24:31.720 --> 24:32.960
I'm so glad I'm not late.

24:38.320 --> 24:40.880
Here you are, Luwei Weiwei!
Where's Yixiao Naihe?

24:41.520 --> 24:42.920
You have to win! We're rooting for you!

24:43.920 --> 24:45.960
Weiwei, I bought a ticket, too.

24:46.040 --> 24:48.840
I hear the winners get
a cut of the ticket sales.

24:48.920 --> 24:50.400
I need to use the bathroom.

24:50.480 --> 24:52.200
- Me first.
- Me!

24:52.280 --> 24:54.840
- Rock paper scissors. Winner goes first.
- No way!

25:04.000 --> 25:06.760
Whether it's for our server
or your own pocketbook,

25:06.840 --> 25:07.800
you have to win.

25:09.840 --> 25:14.040
Thanks. We'll do our best.
Thanks for all of your support.

25:33.680 --> 25:36.000
- What's going on?
- It's a pile-up accident.

25:36.080 --> 25:38.240
A truck malfunctioned
and smashed into several cars.

25:38.320 --> 25:40.480
All the injured were sent here.

25:42.440 --> 25:45.360
- What's his heart rate?
- Heart rate 56, blood pressure 110/150.

25:49.320 --> 25:51.200
Take him to Room One for MRI scan.

25:51.280 --> 25:52.360
- Got it.
- Okay.

25:52.440 --> 25:54.360
Doctor, is my classmate okay?

25:54.440 --> 25:56.640
Mister, please wait patiently
for the exam result.

25:56.720 --> 25:58.320
We'll let you know as soon as it's out.

25:58.400 --> 26:01.120
We need to examine other patients.
Please cooperate.

26:19.520 --> 26:23.200
How come Naihe isn't here yet?
He's never late.

26:32.480 --> 26:33.440
Are you there?

26:36.600 --> 26:38.080
Is Yixiao Naihe going to be late?

26:38.160 --> 26:40.840
It's such an important competition.
Why is he late?

26:40.920 --> 26:42.720
There are 10 more minutes.
What's the hurry?

26:42.800 --> 26:44.880
Master players always arrive last.

27:15.480 --> 27:16.320
Here.

27:18.760 --> 27:19.800
So annoying!

27:20.760 --> 27:21.720
There you go.

27:28.560 --> 27:30.680
It's minutes to go. Why isn't he here?

27:30.760 --> 27:32.120
Is he not going to show up?

27:32.200 --> 27:35.480
Crap! Is it going to be a repeat
of Zhan Tianxia and Diemeng?

27:35.560 --> 27:37.800
Will this pair annul
their in-game marriage, too?

27:37.880 --> 27:39.560
What's going on with our server?

27:39.640 --> 27:40.960
I don't think so.

27:41.040 --> 27:42.240
If they're breaking up,

27:42.320 --> 27:44.360
why would Luwei Weiwei be standing there?

27:44.440 --> 27:47.200
Say, is Luwei Weiwei getting dumped again?

27:49.480 --> 27:51.240
Stop the nonsense!

27:51.720 --> 27:54.200
Maybe he's being held up somewhere.

27:56.040 --> 27:58.200
I'm waiting for you
in front of the NPC by the entrance.

27:58.480 --> 27:59.960
Just come in.

28:00.520 --> 28:03.280
The player is not online.
You cannot get the message through.

28:07.040 --> 28:09.800
What's going on, Weiwei?

28:09.880 --> 28:12.280
You should call Yixiao Naihe.

28:12.360 --> 28:16.080
Is he really not going to show up?

28:25.520 --> 28:28.520
It's not eight o'clock yet.
Naihe will be here for sure.

29:12.600 --> 29:13.640
Where's Nai?

29:14.960 --> 29:16.000
What's wrong?

29:16.320 --> 29:17.640
Say something!

29:18.760 --> 29:20.360
They're trying to resuscitate him.

29:21.280 --> 29:22.920
Is his life in danger?

29:24.400 --> 29:25.400
I don't know.

29:29.040 --> 29:34.800
Nai was unconscious when he went in,
with blood on his face.

29:40.720 --> 29:42.000
It's all my fault.

29:44.440 --> 29:46.840
Why did I chat with him
while I was driving?

29:48.960 --> 29:51.480
Why didn't I see the truck
roaring toward us?

29:53.480 --> 29:54.800
It's all my fault.

29:55.920 --> 29:58.040
Why aren't I the one lying in there?

30:04.800 --> 30:05.880
Calm down.

30:06.440 --> 30:07.920
This isn't helping anyone.

30:09.520 --> 30:10.920
Just wait for Nai to come out.

30:12.640 --> 30:16.200
He's so extraordinary. He'll be fine.

30:28.560 --> 30:31.480
Since Yixiao Naihe
and Luwei Weiwei forfeit,

30:31.560 --> 30:33.360
the title of In-Game Couples
Battle Championship

30:33.440 --> 30:38.520
goes to Gaogaoshanshang Youmeinu
and Anica of Golden Sand Howls Server.

30:42.000 --> 30:43.280
What the heck?

30:43.360 --> 30:45.760
I thought we'd see
spectacular battling today.

30:45.840 --> 30:49.280
- Have we been tricked?
- Forget it. I'm so depressed.

30:49.360 --> 30:51.400
It's okay, poor Luwei Weiwei!

30:51.480 --> 30:54.920
Why pity her?
She had the spot but did nothing.

30:55.000 --> 30:56.600
If she wasn't going to compete,
she should've quit.

30:56.680 --> 30:59.640
She handed the championship
to another server! I despise her!

31:00.680 --> 31:02.160
Why are you saying that?

31:02.240 --> 31:03.360
Just think about it,

31:03.440 --> 31:05.200
if it weren't for Weiwei and Yixiao Naihe,

31:05.280 --> 31:07.080
our server might not make it
to the finals.

31:07.680 --> 31:09.640
Weiwei, don't listen to his nonsense.

31:31.080 --> 31:32.240
Poor Luwei Weiwei!

31:32.320 --> 31:35.040
She ran off like a dog without a home.

31:35.120 --> 31:37.360
She'll never put on airs again.

31:37.440 --> 31:39.920
Hasn't she been dumped by two guys?

31:40.360 --> 31:43.320
Qingqing, we should call you
the master of curses from now on.

31:43.400 --> 31:45.640
You said Yixiao Naihe will dump
Luwei Weiwei.

31:45.720 --> 31:47.520
Then she got dumped!

31:49.080 --> 31:51.240
I almost want to pity her.

31:51.480 --> 31:54.720
Payback is a bitch. I'm so happy.

31:58.120 --> 32:00.000
Yixiao Naihe didn't show up,

32:00.080 --> 32:03.360
probably because he's seen
Luwei Weiwei's true colors.

32:03.720 --> 32:04.560
What do you mean?

32:06.120 --> 32:07.880
I heard it from Zhenshui.

32:08.440 --> 32:12.440
Remember how she said she was rich and
refused to sell the seven-colored outfit?

32:13.720 --> 32:18.120
- In fact, she is poor in real life.
- Really?

32:18.520 --> 32:19.760
How did you know, Yaoyao?

32:20.840 --> 32:23.680
She applied for an internship
at Zhenshui's company,

32:24.080 --> 32:25.960
and she said her handle was Luwei Weiwei.

32:26.040 --> 32:28.320
- Zhenshui happened to hear it.
- Really?

32:29.000 --> 32:29.840
What does she look like?

32:30.880 --> 32:32.520
I didn't see her,

32:32.600 --> 32:35.400
but Zhenshui says
she's not much of a looker.

32:36.320 --> 32:37.880
That means she's ugly.

32:39.920 --> 32:43.880
Yaoyao, when can we go to
Zhenshui's office and see Luwei Weiwei?

32:44.080 --> 32:45.160
Right.

32:46.400 --> 32:48.680
I want to slap her in the face.

32:50.120 --> 32:51.240
Sure.

32:51.840 --> 32:52.680
Here.

32:52.760 --> 32:54.840
Cheers.

33:20.320 --> 33:23.440
How's he doing, Doctor?
Why isn't Xiao Nai out yet?

33:37.280 --> 33:40.960
No way! That's simply impossible.

33:43.160 --> 33:46.640
That's right. It's impossible.

33:47.440 --> 33:52.080
Nai... He's so extraordinary...

33:53.440 --> 33:56.920
No way, I don't believe it.

33:58.840 --> 33:59.680
I don't believe it.

34:14.120 --> 34:17.320
What's the matter, Weiwei?
Are you done with the match?

34:19.120 --> 34:20.960
No way! Already?

34:21.040 --> 34:23.679
Did your opponents run away
without fighting again?

34:26.320 --> 34:27.520
I'll go wash my face.

34:45.000 --> 34:47.400
Weiwei, I have a business dinner tomorrow.

34:47.480 --> 34:51.040
- I might be a little late.
- I'll come a bit late, too.

34:51.280 --> 34:53.719
- Half past seven, at the latest.
- Okay.

35:07.120 --> 35:08.640
What's with her?

35:08.720 --> 35:10.880
Something feels off.

35:11.440 --> 35:13.160
Did she lose the match?

35:13.240 --> 35:16.040
Can it be that? It's just a game.

35:16.120 --> 35:17.520
Should I go ask?

35:17.920 --> 35:18.880
Don't go.

35:18.960 --> 35:22.320
If she lost, asking her about it
will only make her more upset.

37:44.000 --> 37:49.240
Help. I can't run anymore.

37:49.640 --> 37:54.880
- Weiwei, I'm about to drop!
- Hurry.

38:01.040 --> 38:02.280
I'm done!

38:13.360 --> 38:16.120
Weiwei, you've run so many laps,

38:16.200 --> 38:18.080
enough to beep your card 100 times.

38:18.600 --> 38:21.520
Goodness! What's with her?

38:22.480 --> 38:24.360
Maybe it's because the finals
are coming up.

38:24.440 --> 38:26.880
She always turns into a monster
before the exams.

38:27.640 --> 38:31.440
But she was only ever a study monster.

38:31.520 --> 38:33.640
Why a jogging monster this time?

38:33.720 --> 38:36.360
Forget it! I think it's about gaming.

38:36.440 --> 38:37.960
She hasn't been playing her game lately.

38:38.800 --> 38:41.240
She never plays her game before the exams,

38:41.320 --> 38:44.040
because she's worried if she did,
she wouldn't get the scholarship.

38:44.120 --> 38:45.400
Without scholarship,

38:45.480 --> 38:49.200
she won't have money to buy
next semester's CET-6 exercise sheets.

38:50.320 --> 38:51.320
That's true.

38:51.880 --> 38:52.960
I'm beat.

38:53.040 --> 38:55.760
I'm done playing the jogging sisters
with her.

38:56.080 --> 38:57.560
I'm going to the cafeteria. Anyone?

38:57.800 --> 38:59.520
- I'll go.
- Let's go.

39:02.560 --> 39:03.720
Come on!

39:42.640 --> 39:44.040
- Old Xiao!
- Nai!

39:45.080 --> 39:46.000
Nai, you're finally awake!

39:46.080 --> 39:47.960
If you don't wake up soon,
I'll jump off a building!

39:48.040 --> 39:50.800
Seriously! You nearly scared us to death!

39:50.880 --> 39:55.120
Nai, now I finally understand the meaning
of being frightened out of one's wits.

39:55.720 --> 39:57.280
You were sent in for an MRI scan.

39:57.600 --> 40:00.440
A doctor came out
and started shaking his head at us.

40:00.880 --> 40:02.640
The three of us were frightened silly.

40:02.920 --> 40:06.120
You weren't in the operating room.
How could it be so serious?

40:06.880 --> 40:08.840
Why did he keep shaking his head?

40:10.120 --> 40:11.840
What matters is that he's awake.

40:12.680 --> 40:14.520
The doctor said you'll be fine,
as long as you wake up.

40:15.560 --> 40:16.520
How do you feel now?

40:19.000 --> 40:21.000
Right! I'll go get the doctor.

40:24.880 --> 40:27.160
I'm fine. I'm not in pain.

40:27.680 --> 40:28.520
Don't worry.

40:29.400 --> 40:30.840
How can we not worry?

40:30.920 --> 40:32.400
You should've been more careful driving.

40:36.280 --> 40:40.320
Uncle, Auntie, I'm sorry.

40:41.880 --> 40:42.800
I was the one driving.

40:44.360 --> 40:48.360
When the accident happened,
Nai pushed me out of harm's way.

40:48.840 --> 40:50.360
Otherwise, I'd be the one lying here.

40:50.760 --> 40:53.600
Kid, don't be so hard on yourself.

40:54.040 --> 40:56.560
Accidents can't be predicted.

40:57.200 --> 41:00.760
Thankfully, he's awake now. Good fortune
comes after surviving a disaster.

41:01.600 --> 41:02.640
That's right.

41:03.840 --> 41:05.520
I should call our relatives.

41:05.600 --> 41:09.880
- They're all waiting for the news.
- Hurry. Lie still and don't move.

41:15.200 --> 41:17.160
Nai, are you sure you're okay?

41:17.240 --> 41:19.880
Are you dizzy? Are you in pain at all?

41:20.520 --> 41:23.680
Here, look at me.

41:24.680 --> 41:27.840
What's one plus one?

41:29.080 --> 41:30.000
One.

41:32.320 --> 41:36.120
- No! I have to find the doctor!
- Enough! Calm down.

41:36.200 --> 41:38.400
It's obvious Nai is fine now.

41:38.480 --> 41:40.840
He knows you're not worth two cents.

41:42.760 --> 41:45.800
- Wait...
- What time is it?

41:46.080 --> 41:46.920
Five in the afternoon.

41:50.440 --> 41:53.400
You should log in and inform Weiwei.

41:55.040 --> 41:57.920
- Mrs. Nai?
- Wait, given the circumstances...

41:58.200 --> 42:00.320
Why are you still thinking about the game?

42:01.480 --> 42:02.480
Mrs. Nai?

42:05.080 --> 42:07.280
Please don't tell me,
she waited for you all night...

44:36.800 --> 44:39.240
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
